{"TopicId":225407,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Interstellar Communikation","CreatedByName":"Tecorian","CreatedById":232451,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-07-11T09:04:35Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Tecorian","CreatedById":232451,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-07-11T09:04:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes anybody know a mod, which make it possible, to have radio connection to Kerbin at long distances?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nReason simple, actually i play some extra-kerbol-systems, can reach them with halfway realistic ships but have no radio connection to Kerbin.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe something, which simulates a Hyperspace-connection?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTHX for any answer\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Iapetus7342","CreatedById":233205,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-07-11T21:30:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTry the J2X Antenna mod or Near Future eXploration.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KspNoobUsernameTaken","CreatedById":229307,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-07-13T10:39:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou would need a plugin or a hyper-boosted antenna.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou could make a \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Module Manager (mod)\u0022\u003EMM\u003C/abbr\u003E patch for this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KspNoobUsernameTaken","CreatedById":229307,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-07-27T13:47:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, there\u0027s a LaserComm mod in the works right now. Maybe you could get a early build from that?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: Lasercomm mod link:\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002229120\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed5780900567\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/topic/225431-wip-lasercomm-optical-communication-system/?do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:195px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027ll need to build it yourself.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222024-07-27T13:51:05Z\u0022 title=\u002207/27/2024 01:51  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 dy\u0022\u003ESaturday at 01:51 PM\u003C/time\u003E by KspNoobUsernameTaken\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}